channel.title: 317 Command Error
channel.description:
Hey Mopar,
I'm currently in the process of making my own OSRS server, and im having an issue, ive never come across before...
Certain commands are not working for me, such as ::NPC and ::Tele..
When i use the command, i get force kicked and eclipse gives me this server error:
[b]Player Slot 1 slot 0 null Player Hit server.model.players.Client@104d27b0[/b] and [b][Username here] is sending invalid PacketType: 103. PacketSize: 17 [/b] This is also my first time with a PI, so this may be a very simple fix, but anything to point me in the general direction would be awesome thanks!!

item.title: 317 Command Error
item.dc:creator: @fpsnipmob fpsnipmob
item.description:
@fpsnipmob wrote:

[quote=“sk8rdude461, post:2, topic:554792”]The error is quite literal.

Your server doesn’t have anything to handle packet 103.

Packet 103 is the commands packet. So basically, everything starting with “::” in your chat box.[/quote]

Would it be a separate file or within the command file itself? (sorry just started learning packets and plugins)

EDIT: I fixed it, Thanks for the help, yet again Sk8rdude!
